ygData.messageBody:
Well it does not look like there is a tremendous
bunch of people here at this time either, but it does
look like the group is a bunch of well seasoned
Norrathians. I myself am not of a high level, but I have had
many characters in their teens. (though I keep getting
bored and wanna try a new class and eventually delete
them all). If anyone here wants to know some good PK
tactics...I am not a pker usually, but I know some good
pkers, and I have some excellent Rogue and Druid tactics
myself (I am from VZ)<br> Thankyou for the advice offer
